7edad86ff1367","tid":233862,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T23:02:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>借ac開post<br />\nfyp就黎交 你地搞成點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外想問下final model既佔分重唔重，硬係覺得佢同interior design冇乜關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmodel 既作用係用黎交代同解釋你個space<br />\n<br />\n如果做得好,present 出黎會令人更易更快投入到你個space, 變相對整體分數上都有加分</blockquote><br />\n咁姐係就算model製作比較簡陋，個design本身豐富而且preboard同booklet表現到出黎既話，都唔會太影響個分數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我既手工好撚差，個site範圍又大<br />\n所以d細節做得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960cdc9ddec715f400dc63b2c63c6fbf59b57920","tid":233862,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T23:02:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ce9d6f36a33843ef60db55fc65ad3abc1aad7f5","tid":233862,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T23:04:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佔分我唔記得重唔重,但應該仲有一科係用黎評你個model 分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇返張評分標準, 張野應該有提過唔同part 佔幾多%</blockquote><br />\n冇呀屌 佢全部野歸類落ea度咋<br />\n做model真係辛苦過其他野100倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12614cb74933b9ac10c18706e91e6a3005e0ae4f","tid":233862,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T23:05:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"288050994a3d7efd56fda5c43176ea6eb087ebb4","tid":233862,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T23:06:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2f977e56186b30e66937eee3c8d916df3012355","tid":233862,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T23:07:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>借ac開post<br />\nfyp就黎交 你地搞成點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外想問下final model既佔分重唔重，硬係覺得佢同interior design冇乜關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmodel 既作用係用黎交代同解釋你個space<br />\n<br />\n如果做得好,present 出黎會令人更易更快投入到你個space, 變相對整體分數上都有加分</blockquote><br />\n咁姐係就算model製作比較簡陋，個design本身豐富而且preboard同booklet表現到出黎既話，都唔會太影響個分數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我既手工好撚差，個site範圍又大<br />\n所以d細節做得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好老實講,要睇返你tutor係咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你對左佢5 個sem 應該知佢對model 著唔著緊<br />\n<br />\n手工差係差成點先, 個site 企唔企到起身, 係咪是是正正?</blockquote><br />\n結構冇問題既，係某d墻既長度唔啱 整體唔係太貼服姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntutor果關就冇問題，佢著重concept同睇plan rendering果d多，不過其他老師黎評分就唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd580232c074602026abad111b29ce98162810e2","tid":233862,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T23:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佔分我唔記得重唔重,但應該仲有一科係用黎評你個model 分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇返張評分標準, 張野應該有提過唔同part 佔幾多%</blockquote><br />\n冇呀屌 佢全部野歸類落ea度咋<br />\n做model真係辛苦過其他野100倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果陣讀好似有科係專評model 分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我幾鐘意做model<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n慢慢黎,cut board 果陣慢慢界, d 邊位就好靚</blockquote><br />\n我好撚憎做d細緻野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以8成精力都投放係build 3d model，rendering果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貪呢d唔洗對size對得太正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a744eef651c6374ad19911457b7d44dad4ce6470","tid":233862,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T23:13:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2188b7d46092caf38dc831f8e239f36b883e71f5","tid":233862,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T23:14:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88a5e83c3a182269fbe772c782b7054be8da18c7","tid":233862,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T23:16:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>借ac開post<br />\nfyp就黎交 你地搞成點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外想問下final model既佔分重唔重，硬係覺得佢同interior design冇乜關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmodel 既作用係用黎交代同解釋你個space<br />\n<br />\n如果做得好,present 出黎會令人更易更快投入到你個space, 變相對整體分數上都有加分</blockquote><br />\n咁姐係就算model製作比較簡陋，個design本身豐富而且preboard同booklet表現到出黎既話，都唔會太影響個分數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我既手工好撚差，個site範圍又大<br />\n所以d細節做得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好老實講,要睇返你tutor係咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你對左佢5 個sem 應該知佢對model 著唔著緊<br />\n<br />\n手工差係差成點先, 個site 企唔企到起身, 係咪是是正正?</blockquote><br />\n結構冇問題既，係某d墻既長度唔啱 整體唔係太貼服姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntutor果關就冇問題，佢著重concept同睇plan rendering果d多，不過其他老師黎評分就唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只要唔係相差都太離譜冇人會拎個尺慢慢度<br />\n<br />\n實淨,有野睇,見到你點玩個space/features/design concept就已經完成到model 既責任</blockquote><br />\n有d太仔細既部分我冇整到，技術唔夠班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果同d plan有d出入會唔會比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如一d細微既支架數目，屋頂橫樑既數目咁樣"},{"pid":"a4f42cf6c55a12750270b4a6597b5ea56203e421","tid":233862,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T23:17:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote